    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0

    tmp = (wp.sin(0.75) / wp.sin(0.68))
    v2 = wp.sin(v2)
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.26)) + wp.sin((v0 + 0.88 - tmp + 0.06)))
